race.description: The Bright & Shiny Copper Race F&M Handicap
race.comment: SATIN'S LEGACY (8) is a promising filly who took charge a long way out and easily collected her maiden win last start over this course and distance. Will find this harder but she continues to progress and looks up to the task. OCEAN TSUNAMI (11) turned for home worse than midfield before storming home to win on debut over 1200m at Scone last time out. Drops 3kgs after the claim and draws a far better gate so she can build positively on that impressive effort. SHE CONQUERS (2) was never in the race first up, but still found the line fairly well and is sure to appreciate the drop back in grade. LAMBERTINA (7) won easily at Nowra last start and appears capable of taking that next step.
